{"tid":2224730,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"「比吳重儀更離譜」鄭念慈裁判官判案一覧","createTime":"2020-09-30T17:44:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T22:02:14.000Z","uid":240362,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5bafeada9c8e6b021cbc752238abbe5e922cbb34","tid":2224730,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T17:44:15.000Z","msg":"今日:<br />\n裁判官鄭念慈判刑時指，被告以相對較難察覺的動作，絆倒正急步行的警員，屬於偷襲，嚴重程度不亞於明目張膽的襲擊。雖然被告動作較難發現，但「天網恢恢」，過程遭閉路電視拍攝下來。受襲警員傷勢即使不嚴重，但仍有實質傷勢，須請 3 天病假。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n裁判官鄭念慈今在九龍城裁判法院判刑強調，法庭絕不姑息襲警，又稱被告失去工作「咎由自取」，判他入獄兩個月，但准他以加碼至原本<strong><span class=\"red\">保釋金的50倍</span></strong>，以5萬元保釋等候上訴。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">每週報到4次、不得離港、須居住報稱地址，以及每晚10時至翌日上午7時宵禁，並明言擔心判入獄兩個月的被告會棄保潛逃。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n其他:<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">反蒙面法示威被截查 職工盟幹事藏伸縮棍 鄭念慈: 伸縮棍殺傷力強大 可重複使用 判囚4個月<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2183736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2183736</a><br />\n<br />\n文員8.31太子站管有彈弓及螺絲帽 裁定罪名成立 判監1年 鄭念慈:推測被告人有必然意圖對他人造成傷害<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2156102\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2156102</a></span></strong>"},{"pid":"f1ae644873be261e679988f455f14751884847b0","tid":2224730,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T17:45:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c297bb030a03984149f018cbbaa08402a45cff20","tid":2224730,"uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T17:46:19.000Z","msg":"8.3清場案 鄭念慈：不能因鐳射筆難瞄準就排除傷人用途 下月裁決<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">裁判官鄭念慈表示，要裁定涉案鐳射筆是否「攻擊性武器」，主要考慮為被告是否有意圖用鐳射筆傷人，「唔係好難瞄準，就rule out佢嘛」。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n辯方質疑是否單憑被告裝束就能作唯一推論，「是否我全副武裝示威，在身上搜出的任何一件物件，就可以用來傷害他人、傷害警察？」<strong><span class=\"red\">鄭官查問，「喺嗰個時間、嗰個地點，嗰件物件（鐳射筆）的可能正當用途係乜？」</span></strong>辯方回應稱，鐳射筆是普通的文具，不能排除被告忘了執袋、用來照射建築物或提示其他人有警察，反問攜著它身處示威現場，是否就一定用來照射眼睛和傷害警察，又形容用鐳射筆來傷害他人是「不可能的任務」。惟<strong><span class=\"red\">鄭官指：「宜家證供就係話，並非不能傷人，只係好難之嘛。」</span></strong>辯方最後指，鐳射筆是藏在首被告的腰包內，而非拿在手上，可見他沒有意圖用來傷人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1077745\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1077745&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kygOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=93fe3a12\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1077745&h=f4ef71e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1077745</a>"},{"pid":"38666d448676cbff0e99ad645650458b64798ddf","tid":2224730,"uid":230942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T17:46:45.000Z","msg":"鄭官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4270f5e3c07c13f73585ec2e3eb23bdc081c6850","tid":2224730,"uid":54125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T17:49:16.000Z","msg":"弱智唔好學人做官啦"},{"pid":"115072d57de0ac4ad7ff410a226f70a8a3ed10e0","tid":2224730,"uid":318505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T17:50:47.000Z","msg":"念佢老母慈咩，念惡條友就有份"},{"pid":"fd2f7fcb10ab2d5573a2870c23996d47db9806cc","tid":2224730,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T17:55:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b21bd0297579b3ff53e193b74698434111a0a345","tid":2224730,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T17:55:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c76a94e863b56b9bcd0d916ad8d4d31cca56b51","tid":2224730,"uid":202425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T18:03:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ba5f8ad0a1b8f0da9b4fb68b1323df4b77ad4ba","tid":2224730,"uid":121145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T18:05:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88dc447783b81269c829de437b985be11081e15c","tid":2224730,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ba5f8ad0a1b8f0da9b4fb68b1323df4b77ad4ba","tid":2224730,"uid":121145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T18:05:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T18:31:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ced6a69e0469311cce5ade696283fd4fe7aeaa27","tid":2224730,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c76a94e863b56b9bcd0d916ad8d4d31cca56b51","tid":2224730,"uid":202425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T18:03:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T